{
  "stem": "19969.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 183.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I've spoken around the country on this subject.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I've met quite a few.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So that was the only comfort we got out of the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And who was there first or second makes no difference to me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I just don't like him attacking me personally or my company commander or me by people who weren't there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "All these people doing the attacks are people who were not there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were in such shape, they were in such bad shape.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't go around saying we're from this company or this division, you see?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were in such bad shape that they just knew that American troops were there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They say there was no way that we could identify.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, we didn't try to identify ourselves-- no point in it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was such pandemonium and such a strain there that we never even thought about any long-term aftermath about who was there first or who was there second.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Really doesn't make any difference.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The 42nd had some men their. they had about 12, 14.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they got to the prison compound before we did.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we'd been there over an hour before they got there, probably more like two hours before they got there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So-- and they really didn't have anything to do with the liberation as such.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because I had the one that had the troops there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They did not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Their 12, 14 men did nothing except to kill-- they took some prisoners.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they killed those five.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Well, a subsequent investigation turned out there were something like 30, 34 dead German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Books have been written that we killed 500 and something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Actually, it was probably not more than 250 in the total camp when we got there.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
